#### API Summary

#### ProductManagement
* [SysGetProductList](#capi-productmanagement-sysgetproductlist) - Returns the list of products (summary details only) for the specified category (optional).
* [SysReadProduct](#capi-productmanagement-sysreadproduct) - Retrieve the full product meta-data for the specified product.
* [SysCreateProduct](#capi-productmanagement-syscreateproduct) - Creates a new product with the specifed values.
* [SysUpdateProduct](#capi-productmanagement-sysupdateproduct) - Updates an existing product with the specifed values. Pass -1 as the version to bypass version checking.
* [SysDeleteProduct](#capi-productmanagement-sysdeleteproduct) - Delete the product item.
* [SysAddProductPrice](#capi-productmanagement-sysaddproductprice) - Adds a new price to the given product item.
* [SysUpdateProductPrice](#capi-productmanagement-sysupdateproductprice) - Updates (replaces) a price for the given product item.
* [SysDeleteProductPrice](#capi-productmanagement-sysdeleteproductprice) - Deletes a price for the given product item. If the priceId being deleted is the currently active price, the defaultPriceId will be set to -1 (not-for-sale).
* [SysSetDefaultProductPrice](#capi-productmanagement-syssetdefaultproductprice) - Sets the default (i.e. active) price for the given product item.
